WEBVTT

00:00:00.140 --> 00:00:03.060
=The Crow Princess of Fortune=

00:00:03.060 --> 00:00:04.980
=Episode 4=

00:00:05.020 --> 00:00:06.060
Poisoning?

00:00:07.220 --> 00:00:09.620
Your Highness, no one poisoned you.

00:00:10.100 --> 00:00:10.859
I made

00:00:10.860 --> 00:00:13.140
all these dishes myself.

00:00:13.220 --> 00:00:16.180
And this meat was all bought
at the market this morning.

00:00:16.380 --> 00:00:17.499
And that fish...

00:00:17.500 --> 00:00:20.019
That fish was caught right
from our own manor's garden pond.

00:00:20.020 --> 00:00:21.180
It's absolutely fresh.

00:00:26.900 --> 00:00:27.860
Little Princess.

00:00:28.700 --> 00:00:29.420
Keep up.

00:00:30.620 --> 00:00:31.019
Quick.

00:00:31.020 --> 00:00:32.060
Little Princess!

00:00:32.700 --> 00:00:33.580
Little Princess...

00:00:40.820 --> 00:00:42.379
No wonder it's smelly and fishy.

00:00:42.380 --> 00:00:43.820
So, it's the fish.

00:00:45.340 --> 00:00:46.300
What do you mean?

00:00:46.740 --> 00:00:48.459
This pond looks deep,

00:00:48.460 --> 00:00:50.460
but the bottom is full of silt.

00:00:50.540 --> 00:00:52.179
No matter how much water you pour in,

00:00:52.180 --> 00:00:53.579
it's just a stagnant puddle.

00:00:53.580 --> 00:00:54.660
It can't come to life.

00:00:58.180 --> 00:01:00.739
(As I thought.
A formation was set up underneath.)

00:01:00.740 --> 00:01:02.579
(It's designed to gather bad luck.)

00:01:02.580 --> 00:01:05.340
(No wonder
the whole manor is so gloomy.)

00:01:05.380 --> 00:01:07.480
(With something like this here,
it'd be strange if things were good.)

00:01:07.480 --> 00:01:09.020
Just clear the pond, and it'll be fine.

00:01:09.780 --> 00:01:10.300
This...

00:01:10.580 --> 00:01:11.099
I...

00:01:11.100 --> 00:01:12.260
Do as she says.

00:01:12.780 --> 00:01:13.860
Your Highness,

00:01:13.980 --> 00:01:14.580
well...

00:01:14.700 --> 00:01:17.740
Dredging the pond
will take a lot of work.

00:01:18.180 --> 00:01:20.259
Moreover, we are
short-handed in the manor now.

00:01:20.260 --> 00:01:21.579
With a pond this large,

00:01:21.580 --> 00:01:23.059
to clean it out completely

00:01:23.060 --> 00:01:25.620
would take at least a month.

00:01:26.300 --> 00:01:27.460
A month?

00:01:27.980 --> 00:01:29.780
By then, it'll be too late.

00:01:30.100 --> 00:01:32.260
Well, we have no choice.

00:01:45.620 --> 00:01:46.659
Shi,

00:01:46.660 --> 00:01:48.779
don't you find that ear-piercing?

00:01:48.780 --> 00:01:51.660
Ear-piercing? My hearing is poor,
so I can't hear anything.

00:01:53.660 --> 00:01:54.580
What's that noise?

00:02:01.180 --> 00:02:02.060
Look.

00:02:04.740 --> 00:02:05.860
Let's get to work!

00:02:31.500 --> 00:02:32.780
Your Highness,

00:02:33.020 --> 00:02:35.020
the Little Princess's identity...

00:02:36.020 --> 00:02:38.420
Can't you tell what her identity is?

00:02:39.420 --> 00:02:41.100
She is a demon...

00:02:43.140 --> 00:02:46.739
She is the auspicious one who will save
our entire manor from this disaster.

00:02:46.740 --> 00:02:48.060
Exactly.

00:02:49.300 --> 00:02:50.340
Now you get it.

00:02:50.700 --> 00:02:51.500
Remember,

00:02:51.780 --> 00:02:53.219
her abilities must remain a secret.

00:02:53.220 --> 00:02:54.820
You must never let outsiders find out.

00:02:55.660 --> 00:02:56.380
Yes.

00:03:00.500 --> 00:03:01.499
(As I thought.)

00:03:01.500 --> 00:03:04.179
(Someone set up a formation on purpose
to siphon off the manor's luck.)

00:03:04.180 --> 00:03:05.520
(Now that the formation is broken,)

00:03:05.520 --> 00:03:07.580
(the one who set it
will surely suffer a backlash.)

00:03:13.580 --> 00:03:15.059
I heard my unlucky third brother

00:03:15.060 --> 00:03:16.620
picked up a child outside.

00:03:16.660 --> 00:03:19.200
(Xiao Jing, Crown Prince of Tianxuan Kingdom)
I thought she'd be some kind of treasure.

00:03:19.340 --> 00:03:20.220
What's this?

00:03:20.540 --> 00:03:22.420
Are you planning to dig a hole
and bury yourselves?

00:03:33.700 --> 00:03:35.339
(It's actually him.)

00:03:35.340 --> 00:03:37.700
(My jerk father in the mortal world.)

00:03:38.540 --> 00:03:40.060
(Five years ago...)

00:03:40.540 --> 00:03:43.160
(I took on the responsibility
of the Mystic Crow Clan)

00:03:43.160 --> 00:03:45.059
(and was reincarnated
into the mortal world.)

00:03:45.060 --> 00:03:46.259
(Mystic Crow Palace, Celestial Realm)

00:03:46.260 --> 00:03:47.140
(Five years ago)
Suisui,

00:03:47.140 --> 00:03:48.259
you are the Mystic Crow Clan's

00:03:48.260 --> 00:03:50.300
(Mystic Crow Ancestor)
lucky star, a rarity in a hundred years.

00:03:50.300 --> 00:03:53.060
Born with the ability to see fortune and woe,
and to communicate with all beasts.

00:03:53.100 --> 00:03:54.280
This time in the mortal world,

00:03:54.280 --> 00:03:56.420
you must find the person with
the strongest dragon aura.

00:03:59.820 --> 00:04:00.539
Great!

00:04:00.540 --> 00:04:01.420
Found him!

00:04:01.580 --> 00:04:03.140
The one with the strongest dragon aura,

00:04:03.220 --> 00:04:05.860
my fated father is right there.

00:04:06.260 --> 00:04:07.739
I will tell the world

00:04:07.740 --> 00:04:11.540
that we, Mystic Crows, are lucky stars
who can bring blessings and avoid disaster.

00:04:11.580 --> 00:04:13.100
Father, I'm coming!

00:04:18.260 --> 00:04:19.379
Wrong, it's all wrong.

00:04:19.380 --> 00:04:20.620
The timing is wrong.

00:04:21.160 --> 00:04:23.560
(Crown Prince's Manor)

00:04:27.020 --> 00:04:28.140
Hurry, hurry.

00:04:28.620 --> 00:04:29.340
Hurry.

00:04:31.780 --> 00:04:34.100
Your Highness has given birth.
It's twins, a boy and a girl.

00:04:34.140 --> 00:04:36.260
One younger brother
and one elder sister.

00:04:36.420 --> 00:04:37.320
Two of them?

00:04:37.320 --> 00:04:39.520
Didn't the Imperial Astronomer say
a lucky star would descend?

00:04:39.520 --> 00:04:40.820
Why are there two children?

00:04:44.100 --> 00:04:44.980
Your Highness,

00:04:45.020 --> 00:04:47.539
I heard strange celestial signs.

00:04:47.540 --> 00:04:49.780
First there was thunder and lightning,
then a golden light.

00:04:49.780 --> 00:04:50.859
I'm afraid among these twins,

00:04:50.860 --> 00:04:51.859
it's likely

00:04:51.860 --> 00:04:53.660
one blessing and one curse.

00:04:54.180 --> 00:04:55.380
A jinx?

00:04:55.900 --> 00:04:56.899
Yes, Your Highness.

00:04:56.900 --> 00:04:58.379
We cannot keep a jinx.

00:04:58.380 --> 00:05:00.240
At best, she'll bring misfortune
to her parents.

00:05:00.240 --> 00:05:02.260
At worst, she'll destroy
the entire household.

00:05:02.860 --> 00:05:03.980
Take that girl

00:05:04.540 --> 00:05:06.580
and dump her in the mass grave
on the outskirts.

00:05:08.100 --> 00:05:09.219
(You idiot.)

00:05:09.220 --> 00:05:11.859
(I was supposed to be reborn
into the arms of the true Emperor.)

00:05:11.860 --> 00:05:14.459
(But you intercepted me early,)

00:05:14.460 --> 00:05:15.899
(and you threw me away.)

00:05:15.900 --> 00:05:17.280
(I was picked up by Marquis Yong'an.)

00:05:17.280 --> 00:05:19.740
(Because of you, I've almost
lost my life all these years.)

00:05:23.460 --> 00:05:24.700
Oh, my third brother...

00:05:24.860 --> 00:05:26.539
Why must you do this to yourself?

00:05:26.540 --> 00:05:27.700
A cripple

00:05:27.780 --> 00:05:29.580
caring for a stray child?

00:05:29.740 --> 00:05:30.940
Aren't you embarrassed?

00:05:31.020 --> 00:05:32.260
If I were you,

00:05:32.380 --> 00:05:33.819
I would have found a hole

00:05:33.820 --> 00:05:35.620
to crawl into long ago.

00:05:44.080 --> 00:05:47.399
♪Little lucky star,
twinkling with a wink at me♪

00:05:47.400 --> 00:05:51.239
♪Every Chinese New Year day brings
the luckiest fortune slip♪

00:05:51.240 --> 00:05:54.759
♪The God of Wealth favors me,
the Matchmaker ties red strings for me♪

00:05:54.760 --> 00:05:57.720
♪With firecrackers going off,
good things keep coming one after another♪

00:05:58.600 --> 00:06:02.239
♪Make a wish on the very first day
of the Chinese New Year♪

00:06:02.240 --> 00:06:06.000
♪By the second day,
my belly's already round♪

00:06:06.080 --> 00:06:09.399
♪Always talking about dieting,
but the chub never disappears♪

00:06:09.400 --> 00:06:13.440
♪Good food brings joy
and happiness every single day♪

00:06:19.040 --> 00:06:22.719
♪With lucky stars shining bright,
every year is filled with joy♪

00:06:22.720 --> 00:06:26.359
♪I'm bringing blessings to everyone♪

00:06:26.360 --> 00:06:30.079
♪Hands clasped together in greeting♪

00:06:30.080 --> 00:06:33.719
♪May every family be sweet and happy♪

00:06:33.720 --> 00:06:37.399
♪With lucky stars shining bright,
may everything go your way♪

00:06:37.400 --> 00:06:39.319
♪Endlessly flowing♪

00:06:39.320 --> 00:06:45.520
♪Good fortune♪